readme:
# Gandaldf Dark UI theme

A dark UI theme for Atom.

This is a modded version of the default theme for Atom and can be activated by going to
the _Themes_ section in the Settings view (`cmd-,`) and selecting it from the
_UI Themes_ drop-down menu.

![](https://f.cloud.github.com/assets/671378/2265086/c6897dba-9e7b-11e3-945d-551cac610717.png)
